==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɑː(r)mə(r)|-ɑː(r)mə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A person who works the land or who keeps [[livestock]], especially on a [[farm]].
# NATO code name for the Soviet [[Mig]] 17 aircraft.

